Oh I suppose so, I didn't know nothing about her - life before her - no. Oh yes, she'd be a transferrer, the same. She was - she was a transferrer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7999576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6713198\charrsid14555338 What's a transferrer?
