Oh no, not after I was married. Mother'd be - seventy-odd, no, her didn't - no, I don't - no, didn't work after we were married. But - she did work. She didn't work after me father died anyhow. He would - he'd have turned -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7999576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6713198\charrsid14555338 She was still transferring?
