Well - well I can't remember, bacon I suppose and - and jam and - bread and butter and jam and - tell you the truth I don't think I ever had much breakfast when I went to school, I never felt like it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7999576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6713198\charrsid14555338 How would your father manage for his breakfast?
