It varied. Pie some days. Hot pot another day. Chips. Rabbit. Meat puddings we had a mixture.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7999576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6713198\charrsid14555338 What about your midday meal on a Sunday?
