\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14119396\charrsid14555338  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6713198\charrsid14555338 thou labour. Yes. Yes. Pick a needle up, oh - yes, you are wicked 
