n them days it - not like they are today. They had - what sit at the park and - he'd be there, you know - it'd be perhaps Longton, Fenton and - and Basil Fire brigade dong - seeing who was the best one when it was a fire, they'd time 'em how long it'd tak
e 'em get there if it come in see. Yes, competition. That's all I can remember.
